Package com.soprabanking.ips.repositories

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    CommentRepository
    This is the Comment Repository interface which extends the JpaRepository.It accesses the Comment model
    ProposalRepository
    This is the Proposal Repository interface which extends the JpaRepository.It accesses the Proposal model
    TeamRepository
    This is a repository interface this interface extends the JPA repository which is used for fetching the team data from the database.
    TokenRepository
    This is a repository interface this interface extends the JPA repository which is used for fetching the details of the token from token table and in this interface, we fire some queries to fetch the data from the database
    UpvotesRepository
    This is the Upvote Repository interface which extends the JpaRepository.It accesses the Upvotes model
    UserRepository
    This is a repository interface this interface extends the JPA repository which is used for fetching the user data from the database.
